OL,3,CMaternity services suspended for six
OL,4,Cmonths at Westmorland General Hospital
OL,6,FBirthing services at Westmorland
OL,7,FGeneral Hospital in Kendal have been
OL,8,Fsuspended for six months due to
OL,9,Fstaffing shortages.
OL,11,FUniversity Hospitals of Morecambe Bay
OL,12,FNHS Foundation Trust says the midwife-
OL,13,Fled unit at Helme Chase supports about
OL,14,Ftwo births per month and does not have
OL,15,Fthe midwives available to safely staff
OL,16,Fthe unit.
OL,18,FWhile birth services will be
OL,19,Ftemporarily suspended, antenatal and
OL,20,Fpostnatal care plus outpatient
OL,21,Fappointments will continue as normal.
