OL,6,FSue Stansfield, Interim Director of
OL,7,FMidwifery, at the Trust said:
OL,8,F"Protecting our women, pregnant people
OL,9,Fand colleagues and keeping them safe
OL,10,Fmust be our number one priority.
OL,12,F"We no longer have the number of
OL,13,Fmidwives available to safely staff the
OL,14,Funit and its on-call arrangement that
OL,15,Fare in place overnight and at weekends
OL,16,F- despite ongoing work to recruit to
OL,17,Fvacant posts.
