OL,4,Cmonths at Westmorland General Hospital
OL,6,F"Therefore, we are making the
OL,7,Fdifficult decision to temporarily
OL,8,Fsuspend birth services at the unit for
OL,9,Fa period of six months.
OL,11,F"This period will allow us to offer
OL,12,Fsafe home birthing and birth services
OL,13,Fat our other two units, whilst working
OL,14,Fwith maternity teams to review the way
OL,15,Fwe use our colleagues across the
OL,16,FTrust."
OL,18,FLocal MP Tim Farron has started a
OL,19,Fpetition calling for the site to be
OL,20,Fsaved from permanent closure.
