OL,6,FHe said: "I am extremely worried that
OL,7,Fthis six-month suspension will not
OL,8,Fonly impact local mums in the near
OL,9,Ffuture, but it could also pave the way
OL,10,Ffor Helme Chase to be closed for good.
OL,12,F"It is also disappointing that the
OL,13,Ftrust have given just 12 hours notice
OL,14,Fbefore suspending birth services.
OL,16,F"This is a very personal campaign for
OL,17,Fme ` three of my children were born at
OL,18,FHelme Chase.
OL,20,F"This is a very special place for so
OL,21,Fmany parents in our area.
